_sText:
I was aiming for a larger style fy_iceworld type map.

The map supports 64 players with enough weapons for everyone.

the map is roughly 4 times the size of fy_iceworld, has many nooks and crannies in the cliffs to camp. there are snowdrifts and unique barricades to add the cover.

I would recommend 22 - 64 players on this map.

This map took me about 3 - 5 days to complete.

The ceiling is also raised so those low gravity servers can enjoy the map too.
